{
  "uid": "v12-0-sql-expr",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 — SQL Expressions",
  "description": "Demonstrates SQL Expressions (MySQL dialect) running on top of two Prometheus queries. Requires the `sqlExpressions` feature toggle (enabled in .env). Query A fetches HTTP request rates by handler; query B fetches average durations; the SQL expression joins the two and sorts by busiest.",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.0", "sql-expressions", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "ds_prom", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### SQL Expressions\n\n**Enabled by:** `GF_FEATURE_TOGGLES_ENABLE=sqlExpressions` (already set in this lab).\n\nYou can join results from different data sources with a SQL SELECT. This dashboard joins two Prometheus queries on the `handler` label. Panel below is the joined result; the SQL is in the query tab — click *Edit* on the panel."}
    },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "table", "title": "HTTP handlers — rate vs avg latency (SQL joined)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 14, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "datasource": {"uid": "__expr__", "type": "__expr__"},
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"}, "expr": "sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))", "format": "table", "instant": true},
        {"refId": "B", "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"}, "expr": "sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))", "format": "table", "instant": true},
        {
          "refId": "SQL",
          "datasource": {"uid": "__expr__", "type": "__expr__"},
          "type": "sql",
          "expression": "SELECT A.handler AS handler, A.\"Value\" AS req_per_sec, B.\"Value\" AS avg_latency_sec FROM A LEFT JOIN B ON A.handler = B.handler ORDER BY req_per_sec DESC LIMIT 25"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"custom": {"cellOptions": {"type": "auto"}, "filterable": true}},
        "overrides": [
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "req_per_sec"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "reqps"}, {"id": "decimals", "value": 3}, {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background", "mode": "gradient"}}, {"id": "thresholds", "value": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 1}, {"color": "red", "value": 10}]}}]},
          {"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "avg_latency_sec"}, "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "s"}, {"id": "decimals", "value": 4}, {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "gauge", "mode": "gradient"}}, {"id": "max", "value": 0.2}]}
        ]
      },
      "options": {"showHeader": true, "cellHeight": "sm"}
    }
  ]
}
